narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Monique Bautista is a Social Worker, Clinical provider based in Fontana, CA. From 2024-05 through 2024-11, this provider received $89K in Medicaid payments across 857 claims serving 270 beneficiaries, billing 2 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 97% of all billing comes from a single procedure code: 90837 (90837). This extreme concentration is unusual and may indicate specialized services or a narrow billing pattern.
